      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他本来足智多谋，在大理国从政多年，什么大阵大仗都见过了，但这时竟心头烦躁，思潮起伏，拿不出半点主意，眼见周围黑沉沉地，远处隐隐传来几声枭鸣，突然背上感到一阵寒意：",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人参见娘娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑冷笑道：",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "渔樵耕读四人互视一眼，站起身来，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑把手一摆，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑脸上一红，厉声道：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那书生道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "段智兴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "农夫怒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么啦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "樵子急",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不得无礼！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "啊哟",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "常言",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十指连心",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "商阳穴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "锳姑冷笑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个大总管！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑止步回身，冷笑道：",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "定睛看时，只见他身高膀阔、浓眉大眼，正是自己指点上山的郭靖，便问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖躬身说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑哼了一声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "忙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前辈请回！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 718
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "空明拳",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前封喉闭气",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "后挟颈闭气",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好俊功夫！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "只听她说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑前辈，我先谢你救命之恩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑听她提到周伯通，登时身子剧震，厉声喝问：",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "垂首凄然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我妈是给老顽童累死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑听她嘲骂自己，但心中疑团打破，反而欣慰，脸上却仍冷冷的不动声色，说道：",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉愠道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉停步回头，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 790
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我爹爹自知不该迁怒旁人，早将老顽童放了⋯⋯",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉微笑道：",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑双眉竖起，冷冷的道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑嘻嘻的道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 830,
      "line_end": 830
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你别杀我，我教了你罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "七曜九执天竺笔算",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "立方招兵支银给米题",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 842,
      "line_end": 842
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顿了顿，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑在心中盘算了一遍，果然丝毫不错，低声记诵道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 858,
      "line_end": 858
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三人同行",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "团圆半月",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 862,
      "line_end": 862
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她昔年做下了亏心之事，不免处处多疑，当下沉着声音道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉拍手笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 900,
      "line_end": 900
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当下大踏步走去，竹签布得密密麻麻，难以通行，她横脚踢去，登时踢倒了五六根，口中说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 902,
      "line_end": 902
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，咦，使不得，使不得！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 906,
      "line_end": 906
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑心中一惊：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 910,
      "line_end": 910
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也不怕丑，胡赖！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 914,
      "line_end": 914
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打狗棒法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打狗棒法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "旋风扫叶腿法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑暗中只听得黄蓉叫道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 942,
      "line_end": 942
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉年幼好胜，又自恃记心过人，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 944,
      "line_end": 944
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "灵机一动，已有计较，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑正在拔着一根根竹签挪移地位，听了此言，呆了一呆，冷笑道：",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 958,
      "line_end": 958
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉奇道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 960,
      "line_end": 960
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 962,
      "line_end": 962
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 962,
      "line_end": 962
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑哼了一声，道：",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 964,
      "line_end": 964
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉侧过了头，想了片刻，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 976,
      "line_end": 976
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我瞧你还是好好回去罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 984,
      "line_end": 984
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 986,
      "line_end": 986
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "锳姑道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 988,
      "line_end": 988
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黄蓉拍手道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 990,
      "line_end": 990
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打狗棒法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1050,
      "line_end": 1050
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金蝉脱壳之计",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1060,
      "line_end": 1060
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把匕首还她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1068,
      "line_end": 1068
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "那樵子叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快请师叔！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1084,
      "line_end": 1084
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "咕噜的说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阿马里，哈失吐，斯骨尔⋯：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1086,
      "line_end": 1086
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他转头向师弟说了几句梵语，简述郭靖的作为。那天竺僧人道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1094,
      "line_end": 1094
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "说",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "斯热确虚，哈虎文钵英⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1098,
      "line_end": 1098
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九阴真经",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1122,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1128,
      "line_end": 1128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金娃娃来啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 1142,
      "line_end": 1142
    },
    {
